    "description": "<strong>MatchR</strong> is a Match-3 roguelike RPG that combines a battle system inspired by <strong>Puzzle Quest</strong> with the replayability of roguelikes like <strong>Slay the Spire</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016280/extras/8a1866630574a8371667107f7b67bbf4.poster.avif?t=1722345013\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016280/extras/8a1866630574a8371667107f7b67bbf4.webm?t=1722345013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016280/extras/8a1866630574a8371667107f7b67bbf4.mp4?t=1722345013\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MATCH YOUR WAY UP</h2>Battle your way through your colleagues to the big bosses of MatchR. You can win battles using several methods: <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Charging your mana through matches then activating your <strong>skills</strong>, </li><li>Making matches using your <strong>specialty orb</strong> - different for each character - which will deal damage to the enemy, </li><li>Planning your plays around your <strong>character traits</strong> to gain as much power as possible.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016280/extras/2a1c9086937d0c306a7674e42b5ee3b2.poster.avif?t=1722345013\" width=620 height=389 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016280/extras/2a1c9086937d0c306a7674e42b5ee3b2.webm?t=1722345013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EVER CHANGING RUNS</h2>You will begin each run with a single <strong>character trait</strong> and loot or buy new ones along the way. They will help you in various ways such as: giving you boost in powers on match-4s, whenever you use your skills, strengthening your bombs... Find the ones that suit and enhance <strong>your</strong> <strong>playstyle</strong>!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOSE YOUR CHARACTER</h2>With <strong>6 playable characters</strong> and <strong>3 starting character traits</strong> for each, you will find the one that suits you the most, and with <strong>costumes</strong> and <strong>backgrounds</strong> to unlock, they will even look different every run!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016280/extras/0c0a4f7977e8415ef9296c8dd8fced30.poster.avif?t=1722345013\" width=620 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2016280/extras/0c0a4f7977e8415ef9296c8dd8fced30.webm?t=1722345013\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STICKER COLLECTIONS</h2>You will be able to spend your MatchR tokens on the <strong>capsule machine</strong> to gain <strong>stickers</strong> between runs to decorate your ID Badge and apply their effects, helping you in the subsequent runs. They range from common to unique, plain to shiny, and even two stickers of the same type can apply a different value or percentage on its effect. You can also find rare misprints reducing the size of the sticker, allowing you to put even more of them on your badge! MatchR rewards finding <strong>perfect stickers</strong>, so keep on trying!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ADAPTATIVE DIFFICULTY</h2>Is the game too easy now that your badge is full of stickers? Don’t worry, you can turn on new challenges which will make your run harder but also more rewarding, so try to put your skills to the test!",
